com.lendico.iban_generator.countries

Interface CountryMeta

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCountryMeta, ATMeta, DEMeta, NLMeta

    public interface CountryMeta
    Each country has its own meta, to valid length, bank code items, branch code items and account and so on, Meta data are set from countries-metas.properties each row represents single country: data in row=Code,Length, left part and right part of the IBAN, .
    Lendicoss
    Author:
    maher
